I know their every move.

9
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:57,557
<i>Which will all become valuable
in good time.</i>

10
00:00:57,724 --> 00:00:59,350
<i>You must trust me.</i>

11
00:00:59,517 --> 00:01:02,854
<i>You must make them want you
as badly as you want them.</i>

12
00:01:06,524 --> 00:01:09,527
<i>- I talked to my mom today.
- How is she?</i>

13
00:01:09,694 --> 00:01:11,112
I don't know.

14
00:01:11,279 --> 00:01:13,198
She's better, I think.

15
00:01:15,116 --> 00:01:16,159
I miss her.

16
00:01:16,326 --> 00:01:20,580
<i>- She's going to be so proud of you.
- Yeah?</i>

17
00:01:20,747 --> 00:01:22,081
I hope so.

18
00:01:22,248 --> 00:01:24,459
<i>Are you ready
to receive your power?</i>

19
00:01:26,252 --> 00:01:29,922
<i>- You know I am.
- Remember, it's a sacred power.</i>

20
00:01:30,548 --> 00:01:34,802
<i>If I give it to you,
you must use it only as I say.</i>

21
00:01:35,136 --> 00:01:37,764
I will. I promise.

22
00:01:37,930 --> 00:01:39,432
<i>Very well.</i>

23
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:42,393
<i>Reach for the mirror,
put out your hands,</i>

