in the city.

47
00:03:52,856 --> 00:03:54,774
- In the state.
- In all the land.

48
00:03:54,941 --> 00:03:57,027
I saw him first.

49
00:06:34,391 --> 00:06:36,852
Here you go, Leo.
Non-fat milk, right?

50
00:06:37,018 --> 00:06:40,105
- Thanks.
- Just don't call me "Mom."

51
